c0310c7c6f28ba9d6d9352fe21ecd0a67ac7b5fc:
query GetJourneyById($id: UUID!) {
  journey(id: $id) {
    id
    goals
    description
    name
    isPublished
    picture
    isPremium
    userCurrentStep
    currentUserCouserStep
    currentUserStep
    steps(orderBy: ORDER_ASC) {
      nodes {
        id
        name
        description
        professional
        duration
        content
        order
        videoUrl
        podcastUrl
        type
        questions(orderBy: ORDER_ASC) {
          nodes {
            id
            options
            questionUser
            questionCoUser
            __typename
          }
          __typename
        }
        __typename
      }
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}

    totalCount
    nodes {
      title
      description
      type
      deadline
      advices
      difficulty
      placeholder
      id
      isPublished
      createdAt
      updatedAt
      date
      notificationTitle
      notificationBody
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
